{"tid":1494541,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣組入] 必須向國際控訴「交人名」白色恐怖","createTime":"2019-08-21T16:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T05:30:37.000Z","uid":9226,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"20906b2f313311cb531f98505764f1a6edd1219f","tid":1494541,"uid":9226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:28:32.000Z","msg":"國泰炒人，機管局炒人，消防被滅聲，準律師被DQ<br />\n<br />\n另外小弟亦都收到消息，共媒零一要求各部門主管交名<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才 懇請文宣組必定要制作不同語言文宣畀世界知呢單野有幾大獲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中共政權不需要出手，只需要向企業施壓炒人，自然就會制造白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n同時要話畀國際社會知究竟中共掌握緊幾多企業嘅命脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等佢地知道其實唔剩止香港，只要你個國家或者企業有同中共密切往來，或者已經賣咗盤畀中國公司，一樣會變成自我審查，從而賠上言論自由<br />\n<br />\n當然唔少得將小粉紅事蹟講出嚟。話畀佢地知就算中國人移咗民，佢哋根本無擁護到自由世界嘅價值觀<br />\n<br />\n請大家幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c9ef84b0571b2ef45f75f1c67e387ca10c13b4","tid":1494541,"uid":9226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:29:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a78e5903ac5570c92488aedd4fc69cd4bdaa46","tid":1494541,"uid":9226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:29:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a1060daf1c73ac431a8cab5b3cf54059db28c6","tid":1