/>\n同時要話畀國際社會知究竟中共掌握緊幾多企業嘅命脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等佢地知道其實唔剩止香港，只要你個國家或者企業有同中共密切往來，或者已經賣咗盤畀中國公司，一樣會變成自我審查，從而賠上言論自由<br />\n<br />\n當然唔少得將小粉紅事蹟講出嚟。話畀佢地知就算中國人移咗民，佢哋根本無擁護到自由世界嘅價值觀<br />\n<br />\n請大家幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"將軍澳砍記者，中共又派人影記者大頭相，我估記者依家係最危險的群體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多人擔心佢地安全，希望文宣組可以關懷記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />提醒下唔好獨自夜晚出街呢啲"},{"pid":"7ee56b8c594b14494345b0db4281622e31c09192","tid":1494541,"uid":168368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T20:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e3cf023235a850b1b5d2b34b21b1b955f2c2ed","tid":1494541,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22db4fb21749cf9fa353e79799441df51c8a46fc","tid":1494541,"uid":9226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:03:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e1b5af9ed6d867d8984d3abc09012961596177","tid":1494541,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:07:42.000Z","msg":"推。"},{"pid":"a14c1726ffa22415df1efee1a45765e1048ec1